Subject: Re: [VB] Re: Welding on Engine blocks

Inexperienced welding on a Type 1 magnesium engine case
will produce enough heat to ignite it, and you won't be able to put  the fire out.
This procedure requires master tig welding skills and the right equipment,
Save the case for your next big party.
Dave \X/


